Ebiten - A 2D Game Library -

- Specialized to develop 2D games
- Headers only (#include "ebiten/ebiten.hpp")
- Minimal dependencies
- Written in C++11 / Objective-C++11


* Platform

- Mac OS X
- iOS
- Android (not yet)
- Windows (not yet)
- Linux (not yet)


* How to use

** Mac OS X without Xcode

Execute the command 'make'.


** Mac OS X with Xcode

(TODO: Write it)


** iOS

See the Xcode project samples/Ebiten-iOS.


